==English==

===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-uːmi|-uːmi]]

===Adjective===

'''gloomy'''

#Imperfectly [[illuminate]]d; [[dismal]] through [[obscurity]] or [[darkness]]; [[dusky]]; [[dim]]; [[clouded]]; as, the cavern was gloomy.
#Affected with, or expressing, [[gloom]]; [[melancholy]]; [[dejected]]; as, a gloomy temper or countenance.
#:<i>Sunday is gloomy,</i>
#:<i>My hours are slumberless</i>
#:<i>Dearest the shadows</i>
#:<i>I live with are numberless</i>
#::'''''Gloomy Sunday''''' (song), lyrics by Laszlo Javor.

